{"tid":2518172,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲流行《上下顛倒泳衣》這樣穿真的可以下水嗎....","createTime":"2021-05-05T23:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T00:49:55.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"832c5a77c01d468c6a443a5297b5bce7b5dce838","tid":2518172,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:59:41.000Z","msg":"夏天到了，當然就是要去海邊PLAY ONE阿！！不過大家的身材.........恩準備好了嗎（笑）不如先來看看鄉民流傳超輕鬆《減肥》法，什麼你說不相信這樣可以瘦？人家都已經有肥宅大變身《只要照著做就會變帥哥》的親身經歷了餒～最近在國外也開始流行一種新泳衣模式《上下顛倒泳衣》。<br />\n<br />\nUpsidedown bikini<br />\n這個名叫Upsidedown bikini的比基尼來自澳洲的比基尼品牌Cantik，他們挑戰了新的泳衣思維，將泳衣整件倒過來穿～是不是相當性感？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWT1Nxhju5sduE79kx2VGPmVz11wBMMnVGjYKepWnkZPw?filename=nucZi9o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnucZi9o.jpg&h=d655719a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW8wDaJ5nQY2qQiN7bbmYpm6uG8fvSjtpjqs1s7KWmixJ?filename=qdXeSup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdXeSup.jpg&h=b3276aea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeRvRVb8wu54rhyhDaVoh96QLHVKjxf897BzR94vb1JQW?filename=bGX6JA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGX6JA4.jpg&h=43ad18a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQzk1j6yLVVPZnu6gFzyLp1XYyAwUsoY176cb521KNddB?filename=ULh6JA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULh6JA5.jpg&h=b2fc7fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSfJdoKE9vamcxQrU1NCbmNAybTNGs48zd7kvdd5vjL5h?filename=3jXKvf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3jXKvf5.jpg&h=60b88b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTL1VJDzWfYYtAEMP5GyQRhbR8mMtMvjTAJfpXWdesDBt?filename=xV8JLPr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxV8JLPr.jpg&h=1b84c023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這款泳衣在澳洲吸引許多歐派的女生來挑戰，為什麼要說挑戰呢，因為........他是直接把繩子綁在胸部上面，代表你沒有料什麼都綁不住！！！對！！他就是歧視沒奶的我們。<br />\n<br />\n不過這款內衣也受到一些批評，許多人認為「穿這樣根本不能下水啊」，水碰到泳衣的摩擦力會瞬間變小，大家起來根本都看光光。"},{"pid":"c0a628eb4788582ce8d9dea6d02af867def60fa0","tid":2518172,"uid":2974,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"以為同條褲調轉"},{"pid":"f4bfad3a2364b20b3effddc0b31e25afe5127670","tid":2518172,"uid":23549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:04:02.000Z","msg":"好多假波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79df6ed0842a5624ae1739decb81a42320241229","tid":2518172,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4bfad3a2364b20b3effddc0b31e25afe5127670","tid":2518172,"uid":23549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:04:02.000Z","msg":"好多假波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:05:05.000Z","msg":"假波夠凸先綁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0612640c28c8c7640dae138f2bbc83629f5566","tid":2518172,"uid":49669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0a628eb4788582ce8d9dea6d02af867def60fa0","tid":2518172,"uid":2974,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"以為同條褲調轉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:06:46.000Z","msg":"+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee985c4a471d2db043cb1c4d975efd76053b2f0","tid":2518172,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:14:25.000Z","msg":"有冇死庫水上下調轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7887a54618efcba037e9305d9c67d8e54099cbd3","tid":2518172,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0a628eb4788582ce8d9dea6d02af867def60fa0","tid":2518172,"uid":2974,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"以為同條褲調轉"},"citedBy